And you query will be looks like below:

```json
{
  &quot;query&quot;: {
    &quot;terms_set&quot;: {
      &quot;tags&quot;: {
        &quot;terms&quot;: [ &quot;JAVA&quot;, &quot;C&quot; ],
        &quot;minimum_should_match_field&quot;: &quot;required_matches&quot;
      }
    }
  }
}
```

